UI DESIGN GENERATION

Design Principles

Clean, uncluttered layouts with ample white space

Consistent card-based sections (bg-white shadow-sm rounded-xl p-6)

Soft, accessible color palette (teal, coral accent)

Clear visual hierarchy via typography and spacing

Subtle animations (fade-down, transition-colors) on load and interaction

Layout & Grid

Use a max-width container (max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-8) for all pages

Responsive flex or grid for multi-column sections:
• Insight buttons: flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-between
• Analytics cards: grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6

Typography

Font family: system-ui, Inter

Headings:
• H1: text-2xl font-bold
• H2: text-xl font-semibold
• Section titles: text-lg font-medium

Body: text-base text-gray-800 leading-relaxed

Labels: text-sm text-gray-600

Color Palette

Primary Teal: #008080

Accent Coral: #FF6B6B

Secondary Teal: #20C997

Background Grey: #F9FAFB

Text Dark: #1A202C

Text Soft: #4A5568

Success Green: #38B2AC

Error Red: #E63946

Components

Buttons:
• Primary: bg-teal-700 hover:bg-teal-800 text-white rounded-md px-4 py-2
• Secondary: bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 text-gray-800 rounded-md px-4 py-2

Inputs: rounded-md border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 w-full focus:ring-2 focus:ring-teal-300

Cards: bg-white shadow-sm rounded-xl p-4 mb-6

Modals/drawers: centered overlay fixed inset-0 bg-black/50 flex items-center justify-center, inner box bg-white rounded-xl p-6 max-w-md w-full

Navigation & Tabs

Top-level: sidebar or header with patient selector and main nav

Patient Details tabs: horizontal tab list with active underline (border-b-2 border-teal-600)

Mobile bottom navigation: icon + label, highlight active with accent background

Icons & Imagery

Use Lucide React icons at w-5 h-5 text-gray-500

Media panels: w-1/2 image/video with object-cover rounded-lg

Placeholder images from Unsplash via direct URLs

Animations & Feedback

animate-fade-down on section mount

hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow on interactive cards

Button press: active:scale-95 transition-transform

Form submission: spinner overlay with animate-spin

Accessibility

Color contrast meets WCAG AA

Focus outlines: ring-2 ring-teal-300

ARIA labels on icons and modals

Keyboard-navigable modals and tabs